description: Oleana`s Garbodor Gigantamaxed at the ancient mural of Stow-on-Side Power Spot in an attempt to capture Goh and Sonia. When Goh was confronted by Oleana`s Subordinate, Goh`s Raboot Dynamaxed to defend Goh and Sonia from Gigantamax Garbodor. Goh`s Raboot was thrown against the ancient mural of Stow-on-Side to reveal the statue.
name: Dustdas (Olive)
